Peter Dada, Akure The Ondo State Governor, Mr Rotimi Akeredolu has approved the appointment of 19 Permanent Secretaries, three Tutors-General, and the state Statistician-General. This is contained in a statement issued by the Chief Press Secretary to the governor, Mr Richard Olatunde, on Monday. While congratulating the new appointees, Governor Akeredolu urged them to see their new positions as a challenge to work more and rededicate themselves to the service of the state. Details laterâ€¦